////////////////////
/// Drivers Used ///
////////////////////

- Please include drivers in WEBINF/lib/[store drivers in this folder]

1. PostgreSQL for backend logic, driver used is version:
	Java 8
	42.7.4
	install link: https://jdbc.postgresql.org/download/postgresql-42.7.4.jar
	
2. jbcrypt for password hashing, driver used is version: 
	v0.4
	install link: https://central.sonatype.com/artifact/org.mindrot/jbcrypt/0.4/versions
	
3. dotenv-java for secure storage of sensitive information, driver used is this version:
	3.1.0:
	install link: https://github.com/cdimascio/dotenv-java/releases/tag/v.3.1.0

4. JSON-java for more organised handling of JSON data, driver used is this version:
	20250107:
	https://github.com/stleary/JSON-java
	
5. Javax mail and javax activation for sending out of email, driver used is this version:
	Javax mail: 1.4,7
	Install link: https://mvnrepository.com/artifact/javax.mail/mail/1.4.7
	
	Javax activation: 1.1.1
	Install link: https://mvnrepository.com/artifact/javax.activation/activation/1.1.1
	